Package: PowerAnalysis
Type: Package
Title: Tumor-Informed cfDNA Variant Validation Using Binomial Power Analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2025-01-03
Authors@R: c(
    person("Manasvita", "Vashisth", 
           email = "mvashist@fredhutch.org",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2280-5980"))
    )
Description: PowerAnalysis provides tools for validating tumor-informed variants 
    in cell-free DNA (cfDNA) using binomial power analysis. The package determines 
    minimum sequencing depth requirements to distinguish true biological negatives 
    from under-sampled sites with sufficient statistical power. It supports 
    categorization of single nucleotide variants (SNVs) as founder, shared, or 
    private based on their prevalence across metastatic sites, and includes 
    visualization tools for publication-ready figures.
